1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,760
[EP. 08] Before We Meet Again

2
00:00:17,880 --> 00:00:20,440
Yeo Reum…is drawing.

3
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,120
I should go startle her!

4
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:23,000
What?

5
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:26,860
Oh?

6
00:00:30,140 --> 00:00:30,900
Oh?

7
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:32,040
Aargh!

8
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:33,080
Did…did you see it?

9
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:33,940
Did I see what?

10
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:35,760
Not…nothing…

11
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:42,680
But geez,

12
00:00:42,940 --> 00:00:43,880
Why did you startle me?

13
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:48,020
You’re just so good at surprising people, huh?

14
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:49,760
Don’t ever do that again or else…

15
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,820
Draw me!

16
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:52,420
What? Now?

17
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:53,520
I don’t feel like it~

18
00:00:53,900 --> 00:00:55,100
Draw me! Now!

19
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:55,960
Later.

20
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,700
Later when? Just draw me now!

21
00:00:57,700 --> 00:00:59,400
What’s going on?

22
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,240
Ok…fine.

23
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,960
Sit over there.

24
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:05,900
He…here?

25
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,200
Hmmm… Not there.

26
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,640
Over here.

27
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,060
Hey, stay still!

28
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,940
I can’t draw you if you keep moving!

29
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:18,380
Smile a bit!

30
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:42,340
Did Wook…look like this?

31
00:01:42,340 --> 00:01:44,740
I’m getting nervous for no…reason…

32
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:51,360
Familiarity; a room to be new

33
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:13,840
A Day Before Us

